Interface ProxyCache.ProxyFactory

  • Enclosing class:
    ProxyCache

    public static interface ProxyCache.ProxyFactory
    Proxy type validator and ProxyCache.CacheHandler creation factory. Validation of each class will only be called once (unless invalidated).

    Elliot Ford
